text:
Marleny, I appreciate your candor. Your experience and perspective is valid and true and no one here would say otherwise. This is a group project. We have not been working from a set of instructions. Personally, I feel that I have given you all the specification I could. Had I provided more specification and a walk through, I would have essentially just created your component with you as a proxy. Which to me is grossly overstepping my role as a team player, and also disrespectful to you as an esteemed colleague.

The reason for the white label error is that there is no GET method supported on the backend for the root page. This is fine, the backend server is not supposed to display anything.
